|Main Hall = Nagare-zukuri, Cypress Bark Roof
|Other names = Wakamiya-sama
|Festival Dates = Closest Friday-Sunday to the lunar October 15
|Rituals = Sacred Procession and River Crossing Ceremony (on festival dates), Horan Enya (early January)
